      "releaseNotes": "We’ve been cooking up something behind the scenes to make the Greggs App even tastier…\n \nGet mouth-watering deals at your fingertips with the new ‘Offers’ page, letting you opt in to tasty rewards in a few quick clicks. Just upgrade to the latest version of the Greggs App for the best experience and new features.",
